alienate
Homonym Number:
Word Class:verb
Sense Number:
Definition:[A freq. use applied spec. to Ma. lands of OED v. 2. to transfer to the ownership of another. 1513; Alienated ppl.a. 1611, with lands, 1876; Alienation n. 2. 1430, with lands 1661.]
